description:
In the very first Everything Iconic POP Dive, Danny & his guest (H. Alan Scott) will deep dive into The Rosie O'Donnell Show. Every Everything Iconic POP Dive will dive into a different iconic pop culture touchstone. For the inaugural special, Danny & H. Alan discuss the show's legacy, iconic moments, & so much more.


*For bonus episodes, join the Patreon at www.Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
